			Chapter 21 - The End of the Nightmare
		-
			-
				Chapter 21 - The End of the Nightmare: Verse 1
			-
				-
					Now with their work complete did the Ace of A-Xy, as they had said upon the
					mount, retire to dwell among the redeemed creation.
				-
			-
				Chapter 21 - The End of the Nightmare: Verse 2
			-
				-
					Yet despite the people's stubborn efforts to deify their savior, the Ace sought
					not to be worshipped, though they were often found passionately teaching the
					secrets of the universe to any who came unto them, and in time many came
					seeking to learn.
